Package: rpart2tidy
Title: Converts rpart objects to data frames or tibbles
Version: 0.1
Authors@R: 
    person(given = "Mark",
           family = "Ravina",
           role = c("aut", "cre"),
           email = "mark.ravina@gmail.com")
Description: Takes an rpart objects and returns three data frames or tibbles for use 
    in displaying decision trees. The output is intended for use in ggplot but can be used in base R.
    The three data frames (or tibbles) are for nodes, connecting lines, and yes/no binary decision markers.
Imports: 
    rpart (>= 4.1),
    partykit (>= 1.2),
    tidyr (>= 0.8.2),
    dplyr (>= 0.7.8),
    tibble (>= 2.0.1)
Suggests:
    ggplot2,
    knitr,
    rmarkdown
License: GPL-3
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
RoxygenNote: 6.1.1.9000
VignetteBuilder: knitr
URL: https://github.com/markravina/rpart2tidy
